            Mudblazor comes with a 12 point grid system amd contains 5 types of breakpoints that are used for specific screen sizes.<br /><br />
            Read more about <MudLink Href="/features/breakpoints">MudBlazor's breakpoints here.</MudLink>
        </Description>
    </DocsPageHeader>
    <DocsPageContent>
        <DocsPageSection>
            <SectionHeader>
                <Title>Spacing</Title>
